---
// About Section - Company overview and values
---

<!-- Company Overview -->
<section id="about" class="section bg-cream">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <div class="inline-block mb-4 px-4 py-2 bg-dark-green/10 rounded-full">
        <span class="text-dark-green font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide">ABOUT US</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-black mb-6">
        Pioneering Sustainable Agriculture
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-black/70">
        HeartsBio is a pioneering R&D company dedicated to revolutionizing agriculture through sustainable biotechnology solutions
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Two Column Layout: Mission + Image -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-black mb-6">
          Our Mission
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-black/70">
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-black">
            Built on 220+ years of collective research experience and a proprietary biobank of 10,000+ microbial strains.
          </p>
          <p>
            HeartsBio specializes in groundbreaking formulations that enhance the efficacy of conventional fertilizers, providing higher productivity while reversing their environmental impact.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our proprietary biobank provides us with elite candidates to produce microbial biostimulants, biocontrol agents, enzymes, natural growth hormones, and metabolites that create sustainable solutions to today's agricultural challenges.
          </p>
          <p>
            Through rigorous research and development, we transform cutting-edge biotechnology into practical solutions that benefit farmers, the environment, and food security worldwide.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
        <img
          src="/images/facility.jpg"
          alt="HeartsBio research facility"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Values -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-black mb-4">
          Our Core Values
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-black/70">
          The principles that guide our research and drive our innovation
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Value 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-dark-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-black mb-2">
            Innovation
          </h4>
          <p class="text-black/70 text-sm">
            Continuously pushing boundaries through cutting-edge research and novel biotechnology solutions
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-black mb-2">
            Sustainability
          </h4>
          <p class="text-black/70 text-sm">
            Developing environmentally responsible solutions that protect our planet for future generations
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-dark-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-black mb-2">
            Scientific Rigor
          </h4>
          <p class="text-black/70 text-sm">
            Maintaining the highest standards of research integrity and evidence-based validation
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-black mb-2">
            Collaboration
          </h4>
          <p class="text-black/70 text-sm">
            Partnering with researchers, farmers, and industry leaders to maximize real-world impact
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-dark-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-black mb-2">
            Results-Driven
          </h4>
          <p class="text-black/70 text-sm">
            Focused on delivering measurable outcomes and tangible benefits for agricultural productivity
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-display font-bold text-black mb-2">
            Long-term Vision
          </h4>
          <p class="text-black/70 text-sm">
            Building solutions today that will shape the future of sustainable agriculture
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
